<h2 class="section-title"><%= @labels['about'] %></h2>
<p itemprop="description">February 2 is Troyhog Day, the spectacular conglomeration of Troy's birthday and <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Groundhog_day">Groundhog Day</a>.</p>
<p>According to folklore, if it is cloudy when Troy emerges from his coding basement on this day, then autumn will come early; if it is sunny, Troy's pale skin will supposedly burst into flames, he will retreat back into the basement, and the summer weather will continue for six more weeks.</p>